[30;1m179 | [0m[35m[0m

[30;1m74 | [0m[35m  them what the minimum/maximum password length is).[0m
[30;1m75 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m76 | [0m[35m  This introduces new translatable strings which haven't been translated yet.[0m

[30;1m254 | [0m[35m  4. return whether password matches[0m
[30;1m255 | [0m[35m[0m
